==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Touchback
<hw>Touch"back`</hw> <pr>(t⟦ucr⟧ch"b⟦acr⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Football)</fld> <def>The act of touching the football down by a
player behind his own goal line when it received its last impulse from
an opponent; -- distinguished from <contr>safety</contr>
touchdown.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

